---
title: Kurti kelionę — sequence diagram
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor KT as Keliautojas

  participant CJV as CreateJourneyView<br/>«boundary»
  participant AFV as AddFriendView<br/>«boundary»
  participant JPV as JourneyParamsView<br/>«boundary»
  participant JOV as JourneyOverviewView<br/>«boundary»

  participant TLC as TripListController<br/>«control»
  participant JC as JourneyController<br/>«control»
  participant RC as RouteController<br/>«control»
  participant UC as UserController<br/>«control»

  participant Trip as Trip<br/>«entity»
  participant Route as Route<br/>«entity»
  participant Prefs as Preferences<br/>«entity»

  participant DB as DB

  KT->>CJV: atidaryti kelionės kūrimą
  CJV->>TLC: initCreateJourney()
  TLC->>Trip: new Trip()
  Trip-->>TLC: trip
  TLC-->>CJV: showForm(trip)
  CJV-->>KT: rodyti formą

  KT->>CJV: pridėtiDraugą()
  CJV->>AFV: open()
  AFV-->>KT: rodyti draugų paiešką
  KT->>AFV: pasirinkti draugą
  AFV->>UC: findUser(email)
  UC->>DB: query(User)
  DB-->>UC: userData
  UC-->>AFV: userFound
  AFV->>TLC: addTraveler(trip, friendId)
  TLC->>Trip: addTraveler(friendId)
  Trip-->>TLC: ok
  TLC-->>CJV: travelerAdded

  KT->>JPV: konfigūruoti parinktis
  JPV->>JC: loadPreferences(travelerId)
  JC->>DB: query(Preferences)
  DB-->>JC: preferencesData
  JC-->>JPV: preferences
  JPV-->>KT: rodyti parinktis
  KT->>JPV: patvirtinti parinktis
  JPV->>JC: saveParams(params)
  JC->>Prefs: merge(prefs1, prefs2)
  Prefs-->>JC: mergedPrefs

  JC->>RC: generateRoute(mergedPrefs, dates)
  RC->>DB: getAttractions(city, prefs)
  DB-->>RC: attractionsList
  RC->>RC: score(attractions, mergedPrefs)
  RC->>RC: rankByScore()
  RC->>RC: fitToTimeWindow(N)
  RC->>Route: new Route(rankedAttractions)
  Route-->>RC: route
  RC-->>JC: route
  JC->>Trip: setRoute(route)
  Trip-->>JC: ok
  JC-->>JPV: routeReady

  JC->>JOV: showOverview(trip)
  JOV-->>KT: rodyti kelionės apžvalgą<br/>[siūlyti maisto planą?]

  alt Sutinka generuoti maisto planą
    KT->>JOV: generuotiMaistoPlaną()
    JOV->>JC: generateFoodPlan(trip)
    JC->>DB: getFoodPlaces(route)
    DB-->>JC: foodPlaces
    JC->>Trip: setFoodPlan(foodPlan)
    Trip-->>JC: ok
    JC-->>JOV: foodPlanReady
  end

  JC->>DB: save(trip)
  DB-->>JC: saved
  JOV-->>KT: kelionė sėkmingai sukurta
